text: Manmohini is a Hindi supernatural romantic television series created by Prateek Sharma under LSD Films. It replaced Kaleerein in its timeslot. it aired from November 2018 through July 2020 on Zee TV for two seasons. == References == == Other websites == * * Manmohini on ZEE5 Category:2010s Indian television series
